{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act43side", "eventName": "紅絲絨", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AD-4", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "一個荒唐的早晨", "storyInfo": "邁克爾回憶起勞拉的墜亡，他想帶瑪麗昂一起逃離地塊。盧西恩越來越確信劇團長就在這裡，他回憶起自己最初想要逃離劇團的理由，堅定了再次殺死劇團長的決心。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g2_setting_rooftop", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道爾頓先生，您竟然真的幫我多要了一場戲……還是空中懸吊的特技鏡頭？", "name": "勞拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前不管我怎麼求斯蒂芬導演他都不願意，您一說他竟然就答應了？", "name": "勞拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1837_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒什麼啦。我是格蕾塔女士親自請來的男主角，斯蒂芬怎麼敢不答應我的要求？", "name": "道爾頓"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1837_1#2$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還是第一次接觸吊鋼絲……一定會好好珍惜這次機會的！我先去準備了！", "name": "勞拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1837_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去吧。", "name": "道爾頓"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1837_1#2$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1837_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "裝得倒是很謙卑，要是我不知道你暗地裡找斯蒂芬想動我主演的戲份，大概就被你騙了。", "name": "道爾頓"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1837_1#6$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1837_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第一次接觸吊鋼絲……正好。", "name": "道爾頓"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1837_1#2$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新人就應該有新人的姿態，就算到時候在天上吊他幾個小時，也得撐住，對吧？", "name": "道爾頓"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1837_1#2$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_warehouse", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉，謝莉！我又新加了一場戲，需要用到吊鋼絲，你可以幫我準備一下嗎？", "name": "勞拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不可能。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你很愛演戲，我也知道你很有熱情，但你這是第幾次新加戲了？你這是第幾次擾亂我為整個劇組制定的拍攝進度了？", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大小姐，你有一點點責任心嗎？我不會為了你這樣輕飄飄的一句話改動整個排期，這個劇組不是你一個人的。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉謝莉，我不是故意要增加你的工作難度，但是道爾頓先生說他已經徵得了導演的同意，這個應該是已經確定了……", "name": "勞拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道爾頓？", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道了。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，謝莉！", "name": "勞拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（道爾頓昨天才和我一起罵你，說你這個新人一點規矩都沒有，怎麼可能今天就好心幫你加戲。）", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（吊鋼絲，是吧……）", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g12_dressingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇，小勞拉，你今天看起來真是光彩照人啊！下一場空中特技鏡頭又累又苦，沒有一個演員像你這麼高興呢……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但現在是我最興奮最幸福的時候了。下一場戲是這部電影裡唯一一場完完整整屬於我的戲份，我一定要把它拍好。", "name": "勞拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，你真是太可愛了。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小心不要受傷了哦，如果實在累得不行就來找我，今天晚上我會一直在自己的房間裡……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊！瑪麗昂小姐，你是來幫邁克爾先生補妝的嗎？", "name": "勞拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我先去做準備了，晚點再見！", "name": "勞拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "見什麼見！", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不、不見……不見……你別生氣啊小瑪麗。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一下子沒注意，你就開始拈花惹草了？我們才在一起多久你就厭倦了？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "演戲的時候就在眉來眼去……喜歡年輕的就去找她啊！幹嘛還跟我在一起？之後的妝髮造型你也讓勞拉幫你做吧！", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別說氣話，親愛的。我對你是真心誠意的。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你真的不喜歡，我以後再也不主動接觸她了，我發誓！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……真的？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你的那點小毛病，但現在正是你事業的上升期，不要做那些蠢事，也不要辜負我對你的心意。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個叫勞拉的年輕女生又吵又愛出風頭，一定不單純，不值得你花心思。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從現在開始，不准主動接近她。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不能跟她說話，也不能有肢體接觸，就算她快死了都跟你沒有關係……聽懂了嗎？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "親愛的？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瑪麗昂的眼神告訴他，她沒開玩笑。"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道了，我答應你，都聽你的。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#4$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g2_setting_rooftop", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#2$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼還沒到我的戲份啊，發生什麼事情了？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#2$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道爾頓先生那裡有些事要處理，片場的人都調過去了，沒有人給我下達指示……你看，還有一個新人被丟在這裡呢。", "name": "工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，真可憐……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#4$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你才不是什麼很有同情心的人，說吧，是不是想搭訕人家？", "name": "工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是你懂我。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我去看看那個可憐的小美女……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小瑪麗早上剛生過氣，我答應過她不再主動接近小勞拉……不過……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓她主動接近我不就好了嗎？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.4, "yScaleFrom": 1.4, "xScaleTo": 1.4, "yScaleTo": 1.4, "xFrom": 100.0, "xTo": 0.0, "duration": 60.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 2.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.1, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 6.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.3, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾抬頭向上看，勞拉纖瘦的身體被吊在空中，汗水一滴滴流下，浸濕了一小片地板。"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女孩的神情有些疲憊，眼神卻依舊堅定，隱隱刺痛了邁克爾玩世不恭的心。"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吊掛繩索咯吱咯吱地發出聲響，邁克爾可以憑經驗判斷，勞拉穿戴的裝置一定有什麼不對勁的地方。"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過——"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那不是剛剛好嗎？", "name": "邁克爾"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小勞拉察覺到情況不對就會主動向我求救。", "name": "邁克爾"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣一來我既會成為她心目中的英雄，順理成章地跟她親熱一下，又不算違反我對小瑪麗發的誓……兩全其美！", "name": "邁克爾"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再多吊一下吧。", "name": "邁克爾"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g2_setting_rooftop", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "勞拉，為什麼……為什麼你還不向別人求助？我不是就在這裡嗎！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wiatear", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經過去了好幾個小時，繩索的聲音越來越不對勁了……這是從哪裡拿來的設備，怎麼會如此老舊？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡……裂開了？在安全綁帶的位置？小勞拉不可能沒注意到啊！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#6$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行，我要提醒她，我要……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "往前走的時候，邁克爾踩到了濕滑的水漬，在聚光燈強烈的高溫中，勞拉脫水狀況越來越明顯。"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是邁克爾永遠無法理解的堅持和熱愛，眼前這個女孩彷彿否定了他從業以來的一切。"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾回頭，發現瑪麗昂不知何時已經站在遠處的牆角，眼神冰冷地看著自己和疲憊的女演員。"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“就算她快死了都跟你沒有關係……聽懂了嗎？”"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾摸了摸頭頂火紅的耳朵，收回了自己的腳步。"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……既然你選擇自己承受代價，那就跟我沒有任何關係了。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#2$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你要學的第一課，小勞拉。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#2$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "永遠不要太認真，哪怕傷害他人也要保護自己，這才是最重要的——", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#2$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wiatear"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 2.0, "ystrength": 7.0, "vibrato": 3.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咯吱，咯吱。"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "頂端的繩索已經拉伸到了極限。"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還不求救嗎？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wiatear_break"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$glass", "delay": 1.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 4.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g12_dressingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊——！！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#3$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾，你怎麼了？你想到什麼了？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#3$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我跟你來到化妝間是要聽你解釋的，不是看你大驚小怪地發神經……", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#6$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫伊拉說，你想離開這個地塊，到底是什麼意思？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#6$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "親愛的，我得帶著你逃離這裡！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#4$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$m_avg_rglk1secretevent_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "重要公告：", "x": 220.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 800.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n維多利亞知名雲遊劇團“猩紅劇團”即將抵達萊蒙鎮，並獻上為期三天的精彩演出，千萬不要錯過囉！", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n門票數量有限，售完為止！", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_county_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你第一次離開古堡，跟著劇團到這麼遠的地方演出吧？", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1841_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "小盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1841_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緊張嗎？", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1841_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……還好，老師。", "name": "小盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1841_1#1$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其他老師們才是主角，我只是一個很小很小的配角，在舞台上絕大多數的戲份也只是旁觀……", "name": "小盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1841_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但當真正的演出在你面前發生，忍住不逃開，並沒有那麼簡單。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子，這是你新的一課。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "關於萊蒙鎮血案的調查公告：", "x": 220.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 800.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n尚不能確定本案與日前經過此間的猩紅劇團具有直接關聯，警方已成立特殊調查組，進一步嘗試尋找其他線索。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g6_towerterrace", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊塔尼亞，魯珀坎大區，某高塔"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clapsolo", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（鼓掌）", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "精彩的演出。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自從順利完成自己第一次作為主角的劇目後，你終於突破了瓶頸。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你頸部細小的黑色結晶被遮掩得不留痕跡。觀眾只認為你是璀璨奪目的主角，卻不知你已成為迫近死亡的感染者。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今，你的表演越來越純熟，你的歌聲越來越震撼人心，盧西恩……幾乎看不出一絲匠氣。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#12$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是誇獎？", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#1$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不走嗎？還是說，你想要在這裡多待一陣子，再享受一下舞台的餘韻？", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "餘韻？", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是指，這些血腥味？", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#4$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wilderness_y", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 0.9, "name": "avg_npc_045_nn_1#1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大哥哥，借過一下，你擋到路了。", "name": "懵懂的孩童"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要過去，我要回家。", "name": "懵懂的孩童"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，猩紅劇團可以收留這個孩子。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收留？", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她並不知曉，自己的家鄉已經不復存在，她並不知曉，此刻自己面前的這支隊伍裡，或許有些人身上還殘留著她至親的血腥味……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宿命的相逢，不是嗎？", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像曾經的你與劇團一樣。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許，我應該讓你來當這個孩子的老師，教她怎樣融入劇團、怎樣擁抱新的人生……教她，重走一遍你的來路。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下台之後，演出繼續？", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，你還記得我說過的話。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，生活本身便是最好的戲劇，宿命的美學從不局限於載體。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 0.9, "name": "avg_npc_045_nn_1#1"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……大哥哥？", "name": "懵懂的孩童"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_045_nn_1#1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1832_1#2$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1833_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩，怎麼樣？", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1833_1#1$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你考慮清楚了嗎？現在的你，應該能決定了吧？", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1833_1#1$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g10_dormitory", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#3$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "清醒了？", "name": "Miss.Christine"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（慵懶的哈欠）", "name": "Miss.Christine"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，怎麼了？", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "固執的澀味……你的情緒。", "name": "Miss.Christine"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難以下嚥？", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也不至於。", "name": "Miss.Christine"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過來到這個地塊以後，你回想過往的次數越來越多了。", "name": "Miss.Christine"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這說明我們正在靠近他。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你敏銳地察覺到了那個統籌的異樣。", "name": "Miss.Christine"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟你一樣。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遺憾的是，我尚未能挖出更多的線索，她的慘劇便已經發生。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你利用了那個攝影助理，故意抖出天災的消息？", "name": "Miss.Christine"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那份文件出現的時機和方式都太過巧合了，女士。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "參演過足夠多的劇目，便不難知曉，當這樣明顯的線索出現在我們面前，它便一定會發揮作用，推動故事往下進行。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道爾頓的死，只是一個開頭。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有的伏筆已被鋪陳，一切的脈絡已被寫定，沒有人能扯回已經拉開的序幕。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯有讓故事來到謝幕前的高潮，作者才會現身。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……而我才能，殺死他。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（哈欠）", "name": "Miss.Christine"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小心一點，盧西恩。", "name": "Miss.Christine"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是說，小心你自己。", "name": "Miss.Christine"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛剛說過，你的情緒，充滿了固執的澀味……這很危險。", "name": "Miss.Christine"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我向你道歉，Miss.Christine。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會讓你忍受太久。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}